{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21704.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story08","chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Wh-wh-wh-what is WITH that woman?!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":104700,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Are you SURE she's a Magical Girl?"},{"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"I don't...I don't know. But for now, we need@to hide..."},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"I hope that Yuu-san goes somewhere else..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"...Hang on a sec."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"I'll be fine on my own. You kids get the hell@outta here."},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"You're not fine. Those don't look like minor@injuries to me..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"She's right!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"What if that scary person from before comes@all the way out here looking for you?"},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"I can't let you two put yourselves in danger."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Don't worry about that! Unlike me..."},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"This girl here would never abandon someone@in trouble, you know?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":104700,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Eh?! I mean...that's not..."},{"chara":[{"id":104700,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"She saved my life once, too!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I'll never forget it! It happened back when I was@still..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":104700,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"...Thanks. 'Preciate the sentiment."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104700}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Y-you don't believe me?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"Nah, that ain't it..."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"It's just...it's exactly like that chick said.@I'm a bad person..."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"I got duped into thinkin' I could make a quick@buck..."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"...and ended up doin' something I can never@take back... I'm the only one to blame here."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"B-but that doesn't mean violence is the answer!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"I can't just overlook that!"},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"Nah... The monster was right."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"If you guys knew who I really was, you'd wanna@kill me too..."},{"chara":[{"id":104700,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Wh-why would you say that?!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Maybe I wouldn't be able to forgive the bad@things you did either..."},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"...but still, that doesn't mean you have to die!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"It's enough if you just regret it, you know?!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameLeft":"","textBg":"shout","textLeft":"You can't make up for anything if you're dead!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameLeft":"","textBg":"shout","textLeft":"Just— why would you say something that@ridiculous?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kuroe","textRight":"C-can you calm down...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801100,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":801100,"lipSynch":1}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"My bad... [chara:801100:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:801100:lipSynch_1]I get what ya mean."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"I won't die. I'll turn myself in."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"Nothin's gonna wash my sins away, but if there's@anythin' I can do to make up for it..."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"Maybe there's nothin' that can be done..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"...but lettin' myself get killed by a monster ain't@the answer either, is it?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"John-san..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"With that outta the way..."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"...I guess the safest place for me right now@is behind bars."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"We'll take you down to the police station in@the morning."},{"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Sorry we can't do anything else for you..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":801100}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"Thanks. That's more than enough..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"effect":"7001_attack02","id":801100}],"surround":"3901A01","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801100,"mouthOpen":1},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"John","textRight":"[chara:801100:effect_7003_damage02][surround:3901A02][bgEffect:shakeSmall]Guh?!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":801100}],"se":"3002_chara_dead","textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":104300}]},{"bgm":"bgm05_event08","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"zOrder":100.0}],"nameCenter":"Yuu","textCenter":"Found you, bad guy!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":390100,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"AAAH!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":400,"pos":0},{"id":390100,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Yuu-san, wait!"},{"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Please! Just wait!"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Why do you have to kill bad people?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Because I'm a Magical Girl?"},{"chara":[{"id":390100}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"And, like..."},{"chara":[{"id":390100}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Magical Girls are supposed to do stuff like@getting rid of villains that hurt everyone."},{"chara":[{"id":390100}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"We exist to do really good things, don't we?"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"—?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"id":390100,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Th-this isn't a \"good thing\"!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Even if John-san IS a bad person..."},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameLeft":"","textBg":"shout","textLeft":"...that still doesn't make it a good thing!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Mmm... What a pain."},{"chara":[{"id":390100}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"I'm really bad at explaining stuff, so I dunno if@I could get my point across..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"pos":0,"zOrder":110.0}],"nameLeft":"John","textLeft":"H-hang on a sec!"},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameLeft":"John","textLeft":"Fine, I'll hand myself over. Not like I'm gonna@escape with wounds like this anyway."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameLeft":"John","textLeft":"Just promise me you won't hurt these kids!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Ehh...?"},{"chara":[{"id":390100}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"What makes you think I'd do anything to@Kuroe-chan?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Ah, that reminds me."},{"chara":[{"id":390100}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"I still haven't gotten the name of the girl next@to her..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":801100,"pos":1}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"effect":"shake","id":390100}],"flashEffect":"flashRed1","surround":"3901A03","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":390100,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"You stabbed me."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameCenter":"John","textCenter":"*Pant*...*Pant*... I SAID don't move!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Ugh, jeez... Talk about annoying..."},{"chara":[{"id":801100,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"John","textCenter":"(She can just...shrug off getting shanked?)"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":801100},{"effect":"fadeout","id":390100}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"","textBg":"shout","textRight":"John-san!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":104700},{"effect":"fadeout","id":104300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"John","textBg":"shout","textLeft":"Book it! Both of ya!"},{"chara":[{"id":390100,"motion":100},{"id":801100,"mouthOpen":0}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Well, um, uhh... Goodbye?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":0.2},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"flashEffect":"flashRed2","surround":"3901A03","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":0.2},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21704.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":1}],"narrationBg":"bg_adv_red.jpg","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":0.2},{"autoTurnLast":2.5,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":0.2},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"*Gasp!*"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
